1
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:34,320
=Hold a Court Now=

2
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:38,140
=Episode 11=

3
00:01:38,850 --> 00:01:39,820
What are you doing here?

4
00:01:41,330 --> 00:01:42,290
What are you doing here?

5
00:01:42,290 --> 00:01:43,540
I came to find Feng Shengli.

6
00:01:44,980 --> 00:01:45,820
You too?

7
00:01:45,911 --> 00:01:47,355
Yeah. I'm looking for him as well.

8
00:01:48,290 --> 00:01:49,410
Do you know where he lives?

9
00:01:50,180 --> 00:01:51,380
I have an address for him.

10
00:01:52,330 --> 00:01:53,930
Why are you looking for him?

11
00:01:54,050 --> 00:01:55,977
The court wants to organize
another mediation.

12
00:01:56,210 --> 00:01:57,290
But he's gone missing.

13
00:01:57,290 --> 00:01:58,770
I thought this case was closed?

14
00:01:58,844 --> 00:01:59,755
Why another mediation?

15
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:01,260
The defendant wasn't even present,

16
00:02:01,460 --> 00:02:04,100
yet we certified a father
and son disowning each other.

17
00:02:04,260 --> 00:02:05,380
Is that reasonable?

18
00:02:07,820 --> 00:02:09,260
Personally, of course I hope

19
00:02:09,380 --> 00:02:10,850
their family can reconcile.

20
00:02:11,260 --> 00:02:12,890
But I can't
get in touch with him either.

21
00:02:12,890 --> 00:02:14,060
Then what are your client's

22
00:02:14,060 --> 00:02:14,890
current thoughts?

23
00:02:15,130 --> 00:02:16,570
Is he avoiding the mediation

24
00:02:16,690 --> 00:02:17,820
and the payment?

25
00:02:17,940 --> 00:02:19,540
Since he promised to pay,

26
00:02:19,780 --> 00:02:20,780
I'm sure he will do it.

27
00:02:20,940 --> 00:02:21,780
Fine.

28
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,170
We'll talk once we find him.

29
00:02:24,610 --> 00:02:25,450
Go straight ahead.

30
00:02:28,620 --> 00:02:31,060
(Lian Mutton Soup)

31
00:02:33,220 --> 00:02:33,980
All of you, enjoy.

32
00:02:33,980 --> 00:02:35,690
If you need anything else,
please tell me.

33
00:02:35,820 --> 00:02:36,450
Sure.

34
00:02:36,820 --> 00:02:39,220
Welcome. Three people?

35
00:02:39,890 --> 00:02:41,730
What do you want to eat?

36
00:02:42,100 --> 00:02:42,730
Take a seat.

37
00:02:42,730 --> 00:02:43,820
Three bowls of mutton soup.

38
00:02:43,980 --> 00:02:44,380
Sure.

39
00:02:44,380 --> 00:02:45,450
- What else?
- Some side dishes.

40
00:02:45,730 --> 00:02:47,380
Do you need anything else?

41
00:02:48,488 --> 00:02:50,220
Please rush the kitchen.
We're in a rush.

42
00:02:50,220 --> 00:02:50,940
Sure.

43
00:02:51,022 --> 00:02:52,644
Please wait. They will be served soon.

44
00:02:59,130 --> 00:02:59,940
Fei,

45
00:03:00,450 --> 00:03:02,260
it's me. I'm back.

46
00:03:05,622 --> 00:03:07,500
Have you been doing well
in the last year?

47
00:03:07,660 --> 00:03:08,730
Why aren't you speaking?

48
00:03:09,010 --> 00:03:10,260
Are you unhappy?

49
00:03:10,260 --> 00:03:12,540
Can you tell me what happened?

50
00:03:13,220 --> 00:03:14,380
Did your parents

51
00:03:14,380 --> 00:03:15,660
ignore you again?

52
00:03:15,660 --> 00:03:17,260
It's fine. I'll play with you.

53
00:03:18,540 --> 00:03:20,540
This lamb soup restaurant is too boring.

54
00:03:20,540 --> 00:03:22,130
Come with me on an adventure, all right?

55
00:03:22,130 --> 00:03:23,660
I found a secret base.

56
00:03:24,540 --> 00:03:25,980
Let's go.

57
00:03:26,610 --> 00:03:28,220
Stop drawing. Let's go, all right?

58
00:03:28,220 --> 00:03:29,130
Let's go. Hurry up.

59
00:03:29,130 --> 00:03:30,060
We must go.

60
00:03:30,260 --> 00:03:31,130
Let's go.

61
00:03:31,290 --> 00:03:32,220
What are you doing?

62
00:03:32,820 --> 00:03:33,690
What are you doing?

63
00:03:35,060 --> 00:03:35,820
Move.

64
00:03:35,820 --> 00:03:36,820
You're not here to eat?

65
00:03:36,820 --> 00:03:37,780
Leave!

66
00:03:37,780 --> 00:03:39,010
Leave! You hear me?

67
00:03:39,010 --> 00:03:39,780
Go away!

68
00:03:39,861 --> 00:03:41,061
Get out!

69
00:03:41,340 --> 00:03:42,100
Help!

70
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:43,450
Fei, are you all right?

71
00:03:43,450 --> 00:03:44,260
Don't be scared.

72
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:45,730
Don't touch me!

73
00:03:45,777 --> 00:03:47,311
Is this the animal you told me about?

74
00:03:47,355 --> 00:03:48,340
Scoundrel!

75
00:03:48,450 --> 00:03:49,410
You are a rapist!

76
00:03:49,410 --> 00:03:51,340
Listen to me. The police
investigated everything.

77
00:03:51,340 --> 00:03:52,220
I did nothing.

78
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:54,010
Rapist...

79
00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:55,820
Can you not imagine things?

80
00:03:55,820 --> 00:03:57,010
The police investigated it!

81
00:03:57,244 --> 00:03:58,540
How dare you cause trouble here?

82
00:03:58,850 --> 00:03:59,850
They are just kids.

83
00:04:00,044 --> 00:04:00,850
What are you doing?

84
00:04:00,850 --> 00:04:01,540
Stop!

85
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:02,940
Don't do this.

86
00:04:02,940 --> 00:04:04,780
Are you trying to fight? Come on!

87
00:04:05,290 --> 00:04:06,170
Are you provoking me?

88
00:04:06,170 --> 00:04:07,780
They are just children.
Forget about it.

89
00:04:08,340 --> 00:04:09,780
Tong!

90
00:04:11,850 --> 00:04:13,170
Why are you here?

91
00:04:13,170 --> 00:04:15,340
Why have you run away
as soon as I wasn't watching?

92
00:04:15,340 --> 00:04:16,980
What's going on? Come home with me.

93
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:17,930
No.

94
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:27,170
Which way should we go?

95
00:04:27,810 --> 00:04:29,700
I didn't expect this place
to be so remote.

96
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:31,340
The phone and GPS signal

97
00:04:31,340 --> 00:04:32,410
are bad.

98
00:04:32,700 --> 00:04:34,490
According to
the previous direction shown,

99
00:04:34,810 --> 00:04:36,700
we should still walk up the hill.

100
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:38,930
Let's go.

101
00:04:39,290 --> 00:04:40,220
Let's go.

102
00:04:44,410 --> 00:04:45,490
I'm so tired.

103
00:04:53,660 --> 00:04:54,700
This way, I guess.

104
00:05:04,490 --> 00:05:05,410
There's no signal

105
00:05:05,780 --> 00:05:07,220
in this place.

106
00:05:08,140 --> 00:05:09,370
There's a house ahead.

107
00:05:09,700 --> 00:05:10,730
Let's take a look.

108
00:05:14,700 --> 00:05:17,370
Tea Garden Village One, No. 12.

109
00:05:17,755 --> 00:05:18,490
It's this place.

110
00:05:18,490 --> 00:05:19,930
This is the address he gave me.

111
00:05:23,340 --> 00:05:24,460
Anyone inside?

112
00:05:24,810 --> 00:05:26,140
I think we can go in.

113
00:05:31,370 --> 00:05:32,490
Anyone inside?

114
00:05:34,020 --> 00:05:35,100
Feng Shengli!

115
00:05:36,050 --> 00:05:37,460
Feng Shengli!

116
00:05:38,980 --> 00:05:40,170
Is anyone inside?

117
00:05:41,170 --> 00:05:42,140
Stop shouting.

118
00:05:42,340 --> 00:05:43,660
I'm sure no one is living here.

119
00:05:45,170 --> 00:05:47,290
But he did give me this address.

120
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:50,020
This is also the address
he gave to the court.

121
00:05:51,540 --> 00:05:53,580
He either left a fake address behind,

122
00:05:53,930 --> 00:05:56,170
or this house is indeed Feng's,

123
00:05:56,170 --> 00:05:57,540
but no one is staying here.

124
00:05:58,610 --> 00:06:00,290
Are you saying that he lied to us?

125
00:06:01,333 --> 00:06:03,533
I'm just making an inference
according to the facts.

126
00:06:07,580 --> 00:06:08,660
What should we do now?

127
00:06:08,755 --> 00:06:10,155
Let's go back to where we came from.

128
00:06:10,222 --> 00:06:12,088
Go to a place
in the tea garden with a signal.

129
00:06:12,133 --> 00:06:14,490
Then, I'll call
my colleagues to confirm.

130
00:06:22,100 --> 00:06:22,930
Let's go.

131
00:06:29,370 --> 00:06:30,340
Close the gate.

132
00:06:37,660 --> 00:06:39,460
Can you stop hanging onto Tong?

133
00:06:39,460 --> 00:06:40,540
Just spare my daughter!

134
00:06:40,540 --> 00:06:41,850
Adults can't protect her.

135
00:06:42,340 --> 00:06:43,610
We are her bodyguards.

136
00:06:43,810 --> 00:06:44,980
Leave immediately.

137
00:06:45,140 --> 00:06:46,688
Otherwise, I'll call your parents now.

138
00:06:46,711 --> 00:06:47,580
Are you going to leave?

139
00:06:47,580 --> 00:06:48,290
Sure.

140
00:06:48,930 --> 00:06:50,140
Just wait!

141
00:06:50,850 --> 00:06:51,930
As long as I'm around,

142
00:06:51,930 --> 00:06:54,540
don't even think about
running this shop here.

143
00:06:55,580 --> 00:06:56,490
Move!

144
00:06:57,410 --> 00:06:58,340
Just wait!

145
00:07:00,980 --> 00:07:02,410
Tong,

146
00:07:02,410 --> 00:07:04,700
stop hanging around
with these hooligans.

147
00:07:04,700 --> 00:07:05,580
Why don't you know

148
00:07:05,580 --> 00:07:07,290
how to protect yourself at this age?

149
00:07:08,020 --> 00:07:08,980
Protect myself?

150
00:07:09,980 --> 00:07:11,810
Does staying at home mean I'm safe?

151
00:07:12,170 --> 00:07:14,100
Is there someone to protect me
if I'm home?

152
00:07:14,170 --> 00:07:15,170
Who?

153
00:07:15,460 --> 00:07:16,540
Who will protect me?

154
00:07:17,700 --> 00:07:19,410
You sent me to a sanitarium

155
00:07:20,290 --> 00:07:21,610
and confined me for a year.

156
00:07:21,610 --> 00:07:23,100
That's not it, Tong.

157
00:07:23,100 --> 00:07:24,370
You were sick

158
00:07:24,370 --> 00:07:26,290
so I sent you to the hospital.

159
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:28,220
Every mother in the world

160
00:07:28,220 --> 00:07:30,250
cares about their children.

161
00:07:31,370 --> 00:07:32,700
You said you care about me?

162
00:07:33,100 --> 00:07:34,660
Why did you confine me in a sanitarium?

163
00:07:35,810 --> 00:07:37,340
Tong, let's not talk about this here.

164
00:07:37,340 --> 00:07:38,700
Let's go back and talk about this.

165
00:07:38,810 --> 00:07:39,810
Come with me.

166
00:07:39,810 --> 00:07:41,410
You and my stepfather, Li Xueling,

167
00:07:41,410 --> 00:07:43,220
are all against me.

168
00:07:43,220 --> 00:07:44,810
You'd rather believe in a criminal

169
00:07:44,810 --> 00:07:45,780
than me.

170
00:07:45,780 --> 00:07:47,290
All of you are worse than Xing's father.

171
00:07:47,730 --> 00:07:49,100
He respects, understands,

172
00:07:49,100 --> 00:07:50,290
and listens to me, at least!

173
00:07:50,290 --> 00:07:51,340
Tong!

174
00:07:51,340 --> 00:07:52,170
Let go!

175
00:07:52,170 --> 00:07:54,220
Tong, don't speak nonsense.

176
00:07:54,700 --> 00:07:57,170
Tong!

177
00:07:58,610 --> 00:07:59,050
Tong!

178
00:07:59,050 --> 00:07:59,580
Xing.

179
00:07:59,580 --> 00:08:01,610
Tong, when did you come back?

180
00:08:01,850 --> 00:08:03,250
Why didn't you come to see me?

181
00:08:03,250 --> 00:08:04,220
Xing's Dad, hi.

182
00:08:05,170 --> 00:08:06,540
I've embarrassed myself again.

183
00:08:06,540 --> 00:08:08,540
Tong's Mom, don't say that.

184
00:08:09,220 --> 00:08:11,610
Xing and Tong are good friends.

185
00:08:11,630 --> 00:08:13,960
She insists on coming here
when she found out Tong was here.

186
00:08:13,977 --> 00:08:15,610
I followed her because I was worried.

187
00:08:18,290 --> 00:08:19,140
Tong,

188
00:08:19,540 --> 00:08:20,730
can you listen to me?

189
00:08:21,930 --> 00:08:23,100
Come back with me.

190
00:08:23,900 --> 00:08:25,170
I'm not going back!

191
00:08:25,290 --> 00:08:27,050
I'd rather die outside

192
00:08:27,050 --> 00:08:28,140
than go back to your house!

193
00:08:28,140 --> 00:08:29,610
What's wrong with you?

194
00:08:29,610 --> 00:08:30,930
Who do you think you are?

195
00:08:31,290 --> 00:08:32,610
Tong's Mom,

196
00:08:32,850 --> 00:08:33,980
calm down.

197
00:08:36,370 --> 00:08:37,460
She just got discharged.

198
00:08:37,650 --> 00:08:39,730
It's normal
for her to feel a little agitated.

199
00:08:41,770 --> 00:08:42,890
Why don't you

200
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:45,010
let Tong stay at my place
for a couple of days?

201
00:09:03,890 --> 00:09:05,890
I remember there's a junction here.

202
00:09:06,644 --> 00:09:08,530
Why haven't we found the exit
after so long?

203
00:09:12,060 --> 00:09:13,530
I think we are really lost.

204
00:09:20,980 --> 00:09:22,250
The signal is weak.

205
00:09:24,088 --> 00:09:25,370
There's no signal on my phone.

206
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:26,460
What about you?

207
00:09:27,250 --> 00:09:28,300
My battery's dead.

208
00:09:34,370 --> 00:09:35,610
What should we do?

209
00:09:36,770 --> 00:09:38,010
How do we find our way out?

210
00:09:49,530 --> 00:09:50,530
It's getting dark.

211
00:09:51,940 --> 00:09:53,060
Let's move forward.

212
00:09:53,460 --> 00:09:54,980
Otherwise, we won't be able to leave.

213
00:09:56,820 --> 00:09:58,220
Hurry.

214
00:10:15,111 --> 00:10:15,940
Are you all right?

215
00:10:15,940 --> 00:10:16,980
I'm fine.

216
00:10:16,980 --> 00:10:17,850
Slow down.

217
00:10:19,460 --> 00:10:20,650
It's a dead end ahead.

218
00:10:23,610 --> 00:10:24,980
Why don't we walk this way?

219
00:10:25,730 --> 00:10:26,650
Sure.

220
00:10:27,010 --> 00:10:27,940
Let's give it a try.

221
00:10:28,530 --> 00:10:29,420
Let's go.

222
00:10:35,060 --> 00:10:36,100
Are you cold?

223
00:10:36,530 --> 00:10:37,980
Why don't I give you my coat?

224
00:10:38,610 --> 00:10:39,490
It's fine.

225
00:10:39,820 --> 00:10:41,650
I think we'll soon find the way out.

226
00:10:41,940 --> 00:10:42,980
I have a feeling.

227
00:10:44,180 --> 00:10:45,370
You are quite optimistic.

228
00:10:48,580 --> 00:10:54,020
♪Until you appear and I see your eyes♪

229
00:10:55,640 --> 00:10:57,190
♪I've decided♪

230
00:10:57,190 --> 00:11:00,140
♪To stay by your side♪

231
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:06,030
♪I want to be in your world♪

232
00:11:06,030 --> 00:11:09,590
♪Everything is no longer faraway♪

233
00:11:12,340 --> 00:11:13,220
Slow down.

234
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:32,650
Slow down.

235
00:11:36,530 --> 00:11:37,420
Be careful.

236
00:11:42,940 --> 00:11:43,850
Are you hurt?

237
00:11:46,010 --> 00:11:46,980
I'm too tired.

238
00:11:47,490 --> 00:11:48,700
I can't walk anymore.

239
00:11:50,333 --> 00:11:51,460
Hold on for a little longer.

240
00:11:54,890 --> 00:11:56,180
There's a house up ahead.

241
00:11:57,844 --> 00:11:58,940
Let's go and take a look.

242
00:11:59,755 --> 00:12:01,266
- Is anyone there?
- Slow down.

243
00:12:01,370 --> 00:12:02,180
I don't know.

244
00:12:02,850 --> 00:12:03,820
Let's go and take a look.

245
00:12:07,340 --> 00:12:08,300
Be careful.

246
00:12:14,010 --> 00:12:14,770
It's empty.

247
00:12:14,770 --> 00:12:16,650
Do you think there are bugs inside?

248
00:12:17,490 --> 00:12:19,370
There are no bugs in the winter.

249
00:12:23,730 --> 00:12:25,250
It's warmer inside.

250
00:12:26,460 --> 00:12:27,490
There's a lamp here.

251
00:12:28,060 --> 00:12:29,530
Let's see if I can light it.

252
00:12:45,850 --> 00:12:47,010
It's quite warm.

253
00:12:47,610 --> 00:12:48,700
Dry yourself.

254
00:12:49,940 --> 00:12:52,100
This is obviously
a hut for the tea guard.

255
00:13:03,060 --> 00:13:05,220
Actually,
I still believe in Feng Shengli.

256
00:13:07,300 --> 00:13:08,460
I don't know why.

257
00:13:08,730 --> 00:13:10,130
Perhaps it's my intuition.

258
00:13:11,490 --> 00:13:13,180
When I was young,
my grandmother told me

259
00:13:13,610 --> 00:13:15,980
to judge a person with intuition.

260
00:13:16,300 --> 00:13:18,060
If everyone judges with their feelings,

261
00:13:18,420 --> 00:13:19,890
how do you uphold the law of society?

262
00:13:21,180 --> 00:13:22,980
Of course, you are right, too.

263
00:13:31,180 --> 00:13:31,940
Come.

264
00:13:32,650 --> 00:13:33,460
Put this on.

265
00:13:33,460 --> 00:13:34,650
It's fine. You should wear it.

266
00:13:34,650 --> 00:13:36,490
I don't feel cold.
Put this on. It's fine.

267
00:13:40,180 --> 00:13:41,180
Thank you.

268
00:13:41,490 --> 00:13:42,420
It's nothing.

269
00:13:50,820 --> 00:13:51,820
Judge Shen,

270
00:13:52,730 --> 00:13:54,220
when we were in the forest,

271
00:13:54,850 --> 00:13:56,300
I noticed you were a little nervous.

272
00:14:09,155 --> 00:14:11,490
I remembered something
that happened when I was young.

273
00:14:13,730 --> 00:14:15,220
When you were young?

274
00:14:17,770 --> 00:14:19,580
Shen Xiezhi, come downstairs and play!

275
00:14:19,980 --> 00:14:22,180
Wait for me.
I'll be going downstairs soon.

276
00:14:22,300 --> 00:14:23,100
All right.

277
00:14:23,850 --> 00:14:24,940
(Back then,)

278
00:14:25,180 --> 00:14:26,770
(my father was still a judge.)

279
00:14:27,010 --> 00:14:29,420
(People always try to
approach him in many ways.)

280
00:14:29,488 --> 00:14:31,490
(They wanted to pull strings
and use connections.)

281
00:14:33,622 --> 00:14:35,530
(When I was young,
my father kept reminding me)

282
00:14:35,770 --> 00:14:37,100
(to be careful when making friends)

283
00:14:37,300 --> 00:14:38,650
(and don't trust people easily.)

284
00:14:39,180 --> 00:14:41,610
(When I was outside,
I shouldn't mention my parents' jobs.)

285
00:14:42,940 --> 00:14:44,580
(Later, I was annoyed by his advice)

286
00:14:44,890 --> 00:14:46,530
(and just spent my life alone)

287
00:14:46,530 --> 00:14:47,770
(without making any friends.)

288
00:14:50,180 --> 00:14:52,850
(One year, I spent my winter holidays
at my grandmother's house.)

289
00:14:53,220 --> 00:14:54,890
(I knew a boy.)

290
00:14:55,770 --> 00:14:57,980
(Both of us spent our time together
during the holidays.)

291
00:14:58,420 --> 00:15:01,288
(We made capes out of
old clothes from the adults' wardrobe)

292
00:15:01,311 --> 00:15:03,420
(and picked up sticks on the road
to be used as weapons.)

293
00:15:03,420 --> 00:15:04,890
(We rolled around in the mud)

294
00:15:04,890 --> 00:15:06,644
(and our faces
ended up covered in snot.)

295
00:15:07,060 --> 00:15:10,060
(We pretended to be skillful heroes.)

296
00:15:16,866 --> 00:15:18,730
(I thought
the childhood of an ace student)

297
00:15:18,730 --> 00:15:20,577
(only consisted of
exam papers and workbooks.)

298
00:15:20,644 --> 00:15:22,311
(That winter holiday was an exception.)

299
00:15:23,130 --> 00:15:24,180
What next?

300
00:15:26,700 --> 00:15:27,890
Later, I realized

301
00:15:28,060 --> 00:15:29,300
my father was right.

302
00:15:29,933 --> 00:15:31,177
Everyone who approached me

303
00:15:31,266 --> 00:15:32,911
had an ulterior motive.

304
00:15:35,060 --> 00:15:36,610
Including that boy?

305
00:15:36,850 --> 00:15:38,180
Did they succeed in the end?

306
00:15:38,288 --> 00:15:40,355
Of course,
they didn't get what they wanted.

307
00:15:47,940 --> 00:15:49,420
(To get revenge on my father,)

308
00:15:50,010 --> 00:15:51,580
(they tied me up)

309
00:15:52,066 --> 00:15:53,580
(and abandoned me in the mountains)

310
00:15:53,580 --> 00:15:54,770
(after they lost the case.)

311
00:15:55,700 --> 00:15:56,820
What happened next?

312
00:16:00,730 --> 00:16:01,700
After that,

313
00:16:03,370 --> 00:16:05,220
I got lost in the forest for two days.

314
00:16:05,650 --> 00:16:08,130
I picked every fruit I could
from the trees

315
00:16:08,130 --> 00:16:09,770
but I still passed out from hunger.

316
00:16:12,730 --> 00:16:14,220
That's really pitiful

317
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:16,420
for a child.

318
00:16:20,650 --> 00:16:22,940
I thought I'd never escape the forest

319
00:16:24,300 --> 00:16:26,250
until a forest ranger found me.

320
00:16:26,250 --> 00:16:28,100
Did your family members
get angry at you?

321
00:16:29,580 --> 00:16:30,730
Not really.

322
00:16:31,180 --> 00:16:32,650
My father said it was a lesson

323
00:16:32,650 --> 00:16:33,933
for me to learn from my mistakes

324
00:16:34,088 --> 00:16:34,890
so I would

325
00:16:34,890 --> 00:16:36,420
be cautious when making friends.

326
00:16:51,490 --> 00:16:52,460
It's snowing!

327
00:16:58,730 --> 00:17:00,100
It really is snowing.

328
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:02,060
This is so pretty.

329
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:04,980
I didn't expect to see the snow.

330
00:17:08,250 --> 00:17:09,380
It's so pretty.

331
00:17:32,810 --> 00:17:33,860
Judge Shen.

332
00:17:34,460 --> 00:17:35,420
Judge Shen.

333
00:17:36,090 --> 00:17:37,050
Judge Shen.

334
00:17:38,290 --> 00:17:39,220
Judge Shen.

335
00:17:40,420 --> 00:17:41,980
I've finally found both of you.

336
00:17:42,530 --> 00:17:43,730
Ms. Qin, why are you here, too?

337
00:17:44,620 --> 00:17:45,770
What happened to your face?

338
00:17:45,900 --> 00:17:46,980
Did something happen?

339
00:17:49,380 --> 00:17:51,090
Your face has been bitten by bugs.

340
00:17:51,688 --> 00:17:53,155
I told you there were bugs inside

341
00:17:53,222 --> 00:17:54,530
but you just wouldn't listen.

342
00:17:54,530 --> 00:17:56,180
I still need to meet a client today.

343
00:17:56,810 --> 00:17:57,900
How can I face them?

344
00:17:57,900 --> 00:17:59,810
It's fine. You just need
to apply some ointment.

345
00:17:59,810 --> 00:18:01,620
Everyone, don't worry. We found them.

346
00:18:01,770 --> 00:18:03,290
All right. We'll head back now.

347
00:18:03,490 --> 00:18:04,220
Sure.

348
00:18:04,490 --> 00:18:05,730
See you at the courthouse.

349
00:18:06,250 --> 00:18:07,180
Sure.

350
00:18:28,140 --> 00:18:29,540
(Hu Aixi)

351
00:18:31,100 --> 00:18:34,060
(Hu Aixi)

352
00:18:34,360 --> 00:18:35,050
Hello.

353
00:18:35,050 --> 00:18:36,380
Where are you two?

354
00:18:36,422 --> 00:18:38,190
Don't forget. You have a divorce case
at 9 AM.

355
00:18:38,244 --> 00:18:40,730
I'll help you cancel it
if you can't make it back on time.

356
00:18:40,900 --> 00:18:42,140
We are rushing back now.

357
00:18:42,140 --> 00:18:43,622
There's no traffic jam in the morning.

358
00:18:43,644 --> 00:18:45,420
We'll probably arrive in
one and a half hours.

359
00:18:52,900 --> 00:18:55,380
(Child Room, In Use)

360
00:18:56,380 --> 00:18:57,180
Fei,

361
00:18:57,180 --> 00:18:59,010
read some books here on your own.

362
00:19:00,577 --> 00:19:02,530
If you are thirsty, have some water.
Drink more.

363
00:19:03,090 --> 00:19:05,330
If you want to go to the toilet
or need anything else,

364
00:19:05,330 --> 00:19:06,570
Call Ms. Ma Da.

365
00:19:06,900 --> 00:19:08,290
Don't open the door for anyone.

366
00:19:09,010 --> 00:19:10,460
Your color pencils are here.

367
00:19:10,980 --> 00:19:12,290
Don't you like to draw?

368
00:19:12,290 --> 00:19:14,090
If you're tired of reading,
you can draw.

369
00:19:14,290 --> 00:19:15,250
Look at this.

370
00:19:15,530 --> 00:19:17,570
It's your favorite comic book.

371
00:19:17,733 --> 00:19:19,180
When I'm done with the court trial,

372
00:19:19,180 --> 00:19:20,620
I'll bring you out to lunch.

373
00:19:25,090 --> 00:19:25,980
Fei.

374
00:19:31,250 --> 00:19:32,980
Don't open the door for anyone.
Remember.

375
00:19:45,900 --> 00:19:47,530
Doesn't Fei have a rehearsal today?

376
00:19:47,530 --> 00:19:48,860
She's just playing a tree.

377
00:19:48,860 --> 00:19:49,770
Using a prop on stage

378
00:19:49,770 --> 00:19:51,180
makes no difference.

379
00:19:51,570 --> 00:19:52,490
The teacher said

380
00:19:52,555 --> 00:19:54,700
she just needed to go on the stage
during the performance.

381
00:19:54,711 --> 00:19:57,244
Otherwise, she might break down again
if she keeps going on stage.

382
00:19:57,530 --> 00:19:58,900
I should let her relax today.

383
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:02,250
Was Fei being influenced by Tong?

384
00:20:03,220 --> 00:20:04,050
No.

385
00:20:04,420 --> 00:20:05,220
Jing,

386
00:20:05,810 --> 00:20:07,010
let me ask you a question.

387
00:20:07,700 --> 00:20:09,700
If you could turn back time,

388
00:20:09,700 --> 00:20:11,620
and Tong's incident
were to happen again,

389
00:20:12,290 --> 00:20:14,180
would you still bring her back home?

390
00:20:15,050 --> 00:20:16,730
If I could turn back time,

391
00:20:17,290 --> 00:20:18,860
I still couldn't see the future.

392
00:20:19,220 --> 00:20:21,290
I wouldn't know
I'd bring hate to myself.

393
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:23,190
I also wouldn't know
I'd cause so much trouble

394
00:20:23,244 --> 00:20:24,222
for Lian Yongjiu.

395
00:20:24,288 --> 00:20:26,755
She will still be alone
without anyone to take care of her.

396
00:20:27,250 --> 00:20:29,490
What else can I do
if I don't bring her home?

397
00:20:31,380 --> 00:20:32,420
Think about it right now.

398
00:20:32,700 --> 00:20:33,980
If this incident

399
00:20:34,244 --> 00:20:36,330
were to happen again
in the exact same manner now,

400
00:20:36,330 --> 00:20:37,250
what would you do?

401
00:20:37,570 --> 00:20:39,010
The courthouse isn't an orphanage.

402
00:20:39,090 --> 00:20:40,530
Judges are not mothers.

403
00:20:40,810 --> 00:20:43,050
Be less kind and more strict.

404
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:45,620
Judging cases according to the law
is what we should do.

405
00:20:45,770 --> 00:20:46,730
As for the rest,

406
00:20:46,900 --> 00:20:48,380
hear less, see less, and care less.

407
00:20:48,380 --> 00:20:49,940
That's how your breasts can be healthy.

408
00:20:51,570 --> 00:20:52,900
I almost forgot about it.

409
00:20:53,380 --> 00:20:54,860
I forgot to take my medicine.

410
00:21:12,730 --> 00:21:13,530
Qin Rui.

411
00:21:25,730 --> 00:21:26,490
We are here?

412
00:21:34,660 --> 00:21:37,940
(Law Firm)

413
00:21:50,460 --> 00:21:51,660
I had a dream just now...

414
00:21:54,900 --> 00:21:56,530
and saw her falling into a snow pit.

415
00:22:26,700 --> 00:22:27,660
You're already here?

416
00:22:28,422 --> 00:22:30,250
Why didn't you pick up
when I called you?

417
00:22:30,900 --> 00:22:31,860
I'm here quite early.

418
00:22:31,860 --> 00:22:32,940
It's not even 8 AM yet.

419
00:22:33,010 --> 00:22:34,200
You're here at a great time.

420
00:22:34,730 --> 00:22:35,660
The court trial

421
00:22:35,660 --> 00:22:37,266
for this case is at nine in the morning.

422
00:22:37,377 --> 00:22:38,330
Go in my place.

423
00:22:39,133 --> 00:22:41,355
I've completed all the
lawyer exchange procedures.

424
00:22:42,810 --> 00:22:43,860
What is this?

425
00:22:43,980 --> 00:22:45,900
I don't even know this case.

426
00:22:45,900 --> 00:22:47,266
How do I become the lawyer for it?

427
00:22:47,377 --> 00:22:48,620
I'm sure you know this case.

428
00:22:49,090 --> 00:22:50,090
Yang Zixuan

429
00:22:50,530 --> 00:22:52,250
and Xu Zihan. Those two babies.

430
00:22:52,250 --> 00:22:54,090
Didn't you write the Statement of Claim?

431
00:22:54,222 --> 00:22:56,490
They've divorced and
gotten back together multiple times.

432
00:22:56,490 --> 00:22:57,620
What is it this time?

433
00:22:57,630 --> 00:22:59,340
(Legal Representation Agreement)
Who knows?

434
00:22:59,380 --> 00:23:00,466
Perhaps the wife's father

435
00:23:00,555 --> 00:23:03,010
forgot to lift the toilet bowl cover
after he went to the toilet

436
00:23:03,250 --> 00:23:04,810
and the husband's father sat on pee.

437
00:23:05,180 --> 00:23:06,620
Perhaps the wife's father

438
00:23:06,620 --> 00:23:09,010
used the husband's father's dentures
to feed his dog.

439
00:23:09,250 --> 00:23:10,490
Who knows?

440
00:23:11,250 --> 00:23:12,810
This whole family

441
00:23:13,050 --> 00:23:14,220
doesn't even live separately.

442
00:23:14,700 --> 00:23:15,530
Let's see.

443
00:23:15,660 --> 00:23:16,860
The first time,

444
00:23:17,050 --> 00:23:19,900
(Zihan bought
the original-flavor chicken)

445
00:23:19,900 --> 00:23:21,140
(and ate the drumstick himself.)

446
00:23:21,140 --> 00:23:24,570
(He only left Zixuan breast meat.)

447
00:23:24,730 --> 00:23:26,570
The second time,

448
00:23:26,770 --> 00:23:29,220
(Zixuan's mother asked Zihan)

449
00:23:29,220 --> 00:23:30,420
(to breastfeed at night.)

450
00:23:30,420 --> 00:23:31,700
(Zihan's mother was unhappy.)

451
00:23:31,940 --> 00:23:33,090
The third time...

452
00:23:33,490 --> 00:23:34,770
What was it?

453
00:23:36,570 --> 00:23:38,290
Red packet during the new year.

454
00:23:38,460 --> 00:23:39,530
(The money Zihan's mother)

455
00:23:39,530 --> 00:23:41,266
(gave is 3,500 yuan
more than Zixuan's mother.)

456
00:23:41,333 --> 00:23:42,900
Zixuan's mother gave more.

457
00:23:43,010 --> 00:23:43,940
You are right.

458
00:23:43,940 --> 00:23:45,380
I always mixed them up.

459
00:23:46,010 --> 00:23:47,770
We are just there as a decoration.

460
00:23:48,250 --> 00:23:49,290
We are just planted there.

461
00:23:49,380 --> 00:23:50,555
Once the court is in session,

462
00:23:50,660 --> 00:23:52,180
both of them

463
00:23:52,460 --> 00:23:54,490
will tell us the reason
during the whole argument.

464
00:23:55,490 --> 00:23:57,730
Why do I not remember
writing their Statement of Claim?

465
00:23:58,530 --> 00:24:00,460
You don't need to remember so clearly.

466
00:24:01,220 --> 00:24:03,010
I've told you to trust me.

467
00:24:03,010 --> 00:24:04,220
In the first three trials,

468
00:24:04,330 --> 00:24:06,420
I spoke fewer than five sentences.

469
00:24:06,810 --> 00:24:08,660
They even said I speak too much.

470
00:24:09,530 --> 00:24:10,700
Help me out

471
00:24:10,866 --> 00:24:12,050
and I'll pay you 2,000 yuan.

472
00:24:12,180 --> 00:24:13,140
2,000 yuan?

473
00:24:13,620 --> 00:24:14,380
Are you serious?

474
00:24:14,660 --> 00:24:15,530
- Of course.
- Deal.

475
00:24:15,770 --> 00:24:16,660
2,000 yuan sounds good.

476
00:24:29,810 --> 00:24:30,460
Hu.

477
00:24:30,460 --> 00:24:31,010
Judge Shen.

478
00:24:31,010 --> 00:24:32,140
Do you have a band-aid?

479
00:24:32,620 --> 00:24:33,940
Band-aid?

480
00:24:35,770 --> 00:24:37,420
Here you go.
Judge Shen, what's wrong?

481
00:24:41,010 --> 00:24:42,090
Do you have other designs?

482
00:24:42,090 --> 00:24:43,090
No. This is the only one.

483
00:24:43,090 --> 00:24:44,660
It's a gift when I bought coffee.

484
00:24:45,250 --> 00:24:46,570
Sure. Thank you.

485
00:24:46,570 --> 00:24:47,900
How did you end up like this?

486
00:24:47,900 --> 00:24:49,860
You're still bleeding. Wipe it off.

487
00:24:50,770 --> 00:24:51,860
Just make do with it.

488
00:24:51,860 --> 00:24:53,330
It makes you look approachable.

489
00:25:04,290 --> 00:25:05,250
Stop arguing!

490
00:25:06,330 --> 00:25:07,700
Please return to your seats.

491
00:25:08,530 --> 00:25:09,420
Sit.

492
00:25:13,290 --> 00:25:15,330
We will now verify
the plaintiff's information.

493
00:25:15,730 --> 00:25:16,940
Please show us your ID.

494
00:25:23,950 --> 00:25:26,830
(Qingcheng District People's Court,
Tianhai City)

495
00:25:48,460 --> 00:25:50,460
(Safety Check)

496
00:25:50,490 --> 00:25:51,250
Next,

497
00:25:51,250 --> 00:25:53,466
may the Presiding Judge
and Panel Judge enter the court.

498
00:25:53,490 --> 00:25:54,490
Everyone, rise.

499
00:26:04,860 --> 00:26:05,620
Please sit down.

500
00:26:08,860 --> 00:26:09,860
Judge,

501
00:26:09,940 --> 00:26:11,980
all preparation work has been done.

502
00:26:12,250 --> 00:26:13,330
We can begin the trial now.

503
00:26:15,060 --> 00:26:16,549
(Yang Zixuan sues Xu Zihan
in a divorce argument)

504
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:17,800
(Qin Rui is their
authorized representative.)

505
00:26:26,511 --> 00:26:27,810
Where's the plaintiff's lawyer?

506
00:26:28,250 --> 00:26:29,620
She's already in the elevator.

507
00:26:29,620 --> 00:26:30,730
She'll be here soon.

508
00:26:33,140 --> 00:26:34,250
I announce

509
00:26:35,330 --> 00:26:37,940
the Qingcheng District People's Court
of Tianhai City

510
00:26:38,330 --> 00:26:39,050
will now...

511
00:26:39,050 --> 00:26:40,050
Sorry.

512
00:26:42,980 --> 00:26:44,010
Sorry.

513
00:26:44,090 --> 00:26:46,010
Judge, sorry for being late.

514
00:26:46,380 --> 00:26:47,290
Thank you.

515
00:26:49,180 --> 00:26:50,380
Her face...

516
00:26:53,022 --> 00:26:54,330
How is it? What's the progress?

517
00:26:54,330 --> 00:26:55,180
Wait!

518
00:26:57,090 --> 00:26:58,140
What is the relationship

519
00:26:59,290 --> 00:27:00,330
between you two?

520
00:27:05,250 --> 00:27:06,490
How much money

521
00:27:06,900 --> 00:27:08,220
did you receive?

522
00:27:08,460 --> 00:27:09,490
We have verified

523
00:27:09,490 --> 00:27:10,700
both our family's assets.

524
00:27:10,810 --> 00:27:12,180
They aren't divorced yet.

525
00:27:12,420 --> 00:27:13,660
Every cent of Yang Zixuan

526
00:27:13,660 --> 00:27:15,420
also belongs to Xu Zihan!

527
00:27:15,420 --> 00:27:16,620
Mrs. Xu, you've misunderstood.

528
00:27:16,770 --> 00:27:18,010
We are not a married couple.

529
00:27:18,010 --> 00:27:19,090
You are not married?

530
00:27:20,090 --> 00:27:21,290
Then, tell me.

531
00:27:21,380 --> 00:27:22,644
What's that on both of your faces?

532
00:27:22,711 --> 00:27:24,140
Look at the band on your face.

533
00:27:24,140 --> 00:27:25,460
They are exactly the same.

534
00:27:25,700 --> 00:27:27,140
If you don't eat

535
00:27:27,140 --> 00:27:28,090
and sleep together,

536
00:27:28,090 --> 00:27:29,533
how can there be such a coincidence?

537
00:27:29,577 --> 00:27:30,380
Enough.

538
00:27:30,380 --> 00:27:31,420
You have a dirty heart,

539
00:27:31,420 --> 00:27:32,900
so everything looks foul to you.

540
00:27:33,050 --> 00:27:35,090
With no evidence, what
nonsense are you talking about?

541
00:27:35,090 --> 00:27:36,050
Shut up!

542
00:27:36,220 --> 00:27:37,660
I'm sure you know what I mean.

543
00:27:37,660 --> 00:27:39,220
Mrs. Xu, you've really misunderstood.

544
00:27:39,220 --> 00:27:40,530
Defendant, mind your attitude.

545
00:27:40,577 --> 00:27:42,111
If you disrupt the order of the court,

546
00:27:42,133 --> 00:27:42,900
I'll summon the bailiff.

547
00:27:42,900 --> 00:27:44,860
Can I not talk about them
when they are so vulgar?

548
00:27:45,050 --> 00:27:46,290
Isn't it just a band-aid?

549
00:27:46,290 --> 00:27:47,420
I'll just remove it.

550
00:27:47,420 --> 00:27:48,660
Put it back on.

551
00:27:48,733 --> 00:27:50,090
Are you trying to destroy evidence?

552
00:27:50,090 --> 00:27:51,488
I'm going to film this as evidence.

553
00:27:51,860 --> 00:27:52,810
Summon the bailiff.

554
00:27:53,180 --> 00:27:54,900
What are you doing? Stop filming.

555
00:27:54,900 --> 00:27:55,700
Stop filming.

556
00:27:55,700 --> 00:27:56,770
Please don't take pictures.

557
00:27:57,220 --> 00:27:58,620
Both of them are working together!

558
00:27:59,010 --> 00:28:00,050
They are working together!

559
00:28:00,250 --> 00:28:01,570
The judge and lawyer

560
00:28:01,570 --> 00:28:02,860
are working together!

561
00:28:02,860 --> 00:28:04,000
(Court 1, Camera 2)
Everyone, look!

562
00:28:04,066 --> 00:28:05,010
Can't you see?

563
00:28:05,090 --> 00:28:06,250
Are you afraid of being filmed?

564
00:28:06,250 --> 00:28:07,810
Everyone, look!

565
00:28:07,810 --> 00:28:08,570
Look!

566
00:28:08,570 --> 00:28:10,140
You don't let people film in court?

567
00:28:17,490 --> 00:28:18,660
Working together?

568
00:28:19,570 --> 00:28:20,770
You and Shen Xiezhi?

569
00:28:21,860 --> 00:28:22,730
Seriously,

570
00:28:22,860 --> 00:28:24,860
Mrs. Xu has good taste.

571
00:28:25,050 --> 00:28:26,050
Honestly speaking,

572
00:28:26,380 --> 00:28:28,490
the first time
I saw you and Shen Xiezhi,

573
00:28:28,670 --> 00:28:30,200
I knew something was off about you two.

574
00:28:30,420 --> 00:28:32,220
I think you should check your eyes.

575
00:28:34,180 --> 00:28:35,180
You don't believe me?

576
00:28:37,530 --> 00:28:39,620
Have you watched
those lovey-dovey dramas?

577
00:28:45,290 --> 00:28:47,220
Let me analyze the situation for you.

578
00:28:47,530 --> 00:28:48,770
Right now,

579
00:28:48,860 --> 00:28:50,530
both of you

580
00:28:50,530 --> 00:28:52,250
are at the end of the first stage.

581
00:28:52,420 --> 00:28:54,250
At the beginning of the second round,

582
00:28:54,460 --> 00:28:56,860
both of you fancy each other,
but still don't know it yet.

583
00:29:00,090 --> 00:29:01,050
Now,

584
00:29:01,220 --> 00:29:03,530
the male lead should be

585
00:29:03,666 --> 00:29:05,622
complaining about you
with his buddy right now.

586
00:29:06,090 --> 00:29:07,770
Not bad.

587
00:29:08,290 --> 00:29:09,530
I haven't seen you for a few days

588
00:29:09,680 --> 00:29:11,644
and you're already
working with another woman.

589
00:29:12,022 --> 00:29:13,590
I'm sure you've accepted a lot of money.

590
00:29:14,530 --> 00:29:15,620
Why didn't you tell me

591
00:29:15,620 --> 00:29:16,770
about such a good deal?

592
00:29:19,940 --> 00:29:21,330
The inspector came to talk to me.

593
00:29:21,530 --> 00:29:23,250
It looks like a sentence of 20 years.

594
00:29:23,860 --> 00:29:26,250
Buddy, do you want
to share the sentence with me?

595
00:29:26,250 --> 00:29:27,330
Forget about it.

596
00:29:28,010 --> 00:29:30,180
Tell me where you keep the money.

597
00:29:30,330 --> 00:29:31,220
When you're in jail,

598
00:29:31,220 --> 00:29:33,660
I'll visit you every year
with two taels of pork.

599
00:29:35,660 --> 00:29:37,660
You are a High Court judge.

600
00:29:38,220 --> 00:29:39,330
Is that all you've got?

601
00:29:39,490 --> 00:29:40,770
Look at your belief and resolve.

602
00:29:40,860 --> 00:29:42,330
Don't joke around with my profession.

603
00:29:42,460 --> 00:29:43,733
I'll sue you for defamation.

604
00:29:45,570 --> 00:29:48,010
Look, if you hadn't accepted any money,

605
00:29:48,010 --> 00:29:49,140
why did you do it?

606
00:29:49,244 --> 00:29:50,290
Or did that female lawyer

607
00:29:50,290 --> 00:29:51,980
take all your money?

608
00:29:53,090 --> 00:29:54,730
Who's that woman?

609
00:29:54,900 --> 00:29:56,090
Is she really that charming?

610
00:29:56,177 --> 00:29:58,288
She even made our Judge Shen,
who is free of worldly desires

611
00:29:58,333 --> 00:29:59,933
and untainted by the ways of the world,

612
00:29:59,940 --> 00:30:00,700
lose his discipline.

613
00:30:00,700 --> 00:30:03,180
Both of you have slept together.

614
00:30:03,380 --> 00:30:05,700
A man and a woman
staying together alone.

615
00:30:05,980 --> 00:30:07,620
According to logic...

616
00:30:11,620 --> 00:30:12,530
What are you doing?

617
00:30:12,620 --> 00:30:14,010
Don't move. Wait.

618
00:30:17,860 --> 00:30:19,220
This is bad. You're in danger.

619
00:30:19,700 --> 00:30:20,180
Look.

620
00:30:20,180 --> 00:30:21,620
Your hormones are a mess.

621
00:30:21,620 --> 00:30:22,490
Look.

622
00:30:25,490 --> 00:30:27,980
Not just in danger.
I've totally fallen for him.

623
00:30:28,180 --> 00:30:29,140
I should bring my ID

624
00:30:29,140 --> 00:30:31,422
and go to Qingcheng Court
to force Shen Xiezhi to marry me.

625
00:30:31,570 --> 00:30:32,770
He must support us.

626
00:30:32,770 --> 00:30:33,900
How much money per month?

627
00:30:33,900 --> 00:30:36,180
I'm sure half of his salary
is at least 6,000 yuan.

628
00:30:36,377 --> 00:30:37,530
We'll ask him for 6,000 yuan.

629
00:30:37,530 --> 00:30:39,940
4,000 yuan for the rent
and the remaining 2,000 yuan

630
00:30:39,940 --> 00:30:41,688
will be our living expenses for a month.

631
00:30:41,755 --> 00:30:42,290
Right?

632
00:30:42,570 --> 00:30:44,050
Do you not have any feelings

633
00:30:44,050 --> 00:30:45,810
for the female lawyer at all?

634
00:30:46,222 --> 00:30:48,570
Why do I feel like this isn't over yet
between you two?

635
00:30:48,980 --> 00:30:50,420
You tell me!

636
00:30:50,860 --> 00:30:52,330
She's a lawyer. I'm a judge.

637
00:30:52,330 --> 00:30:54,290
We'll surely see each other at work.

638
00:30:54,290 --> 00:30:56,420
No.

639
00:30:57,900 --> 00:30:59,940
You are still too naive, my girl.

640
00:31:00,090 --> 00:31:02,180
This is a good opportunity
to cling to him.

641
00:31:02,420 --> 00:31:04,940
Even if you don't ask him
for a car or a house,

642
00:31:05,050 --> 00:31:07,377
you should ask him
for more living expenses, at least.

643
00:31:08,010 --> 00:31:10,380
You sacrificed your reputation once.

644
00:31:10,380 --> 00:31:11,940
If you have a child,

645
00:31:12,180 --> 00:31:15,330
you'll have to exchange it
for a comfortable life.

646
00:31:17,660 --> 00:31:18,980
Just eat.

647
00:31:19,380 --> 00:31:21,380
Did you read too many web novels

648
00:31:21,511 --> 00:31:23,380
and start making up
your own awkward stories?

649
00:31:39,330 --> 00:31:40,290
This kid

650
00:31:40,810 --> 00:31:42,220
always causes trouble for himself.

651
00:31:43,250 --> 00:31:44,250
What happened again?

652
00:31:45,730 --> 00:31:46,860
Eat. It's nothing serious.

653
00:31:48,730 --> 00:31:50,140
Didn't we agree to it previously?

654
00:31:50,730 --> 00:31:53,140
Xiezhi is your son,
but he is also my son.

655
00:31:53,460 --> 00:31:54,711
If something happens to him,

656
00:31:54,860 --> 00:31:55,860
I need to know, too.

657
00:31:56,050 --> 00:31:57,980
I need to be the first one to know.

658
00:31:59,570 --> 00:32:01,220
Both of you are hiding from me, right?

659
00:32:03,050 --> 00:32:04,420
It's not right

660
00:32:04,940 --> 00:32:06,730
to hide things
about my grandson from me.

661
00:32:07,490 --> 00:32:08,290
Fine.

662
00:32:08,530 --> 00:32:09,570
If there's anything,

663
00:32:10,330 --> 00:32:12,220
I'll tell you both at once.

664
00:32:12,860 --> 00:32:13,700
How's that?

665
00:32:14,140 --> 00:32:16,860
Everyone is
talking about Xiezhi's incident now.

666
00:32:19,530 --> 00:32:20,660
The party made a complaint

667
00:32:21,090 --> 00:32:24,140
claiming that Shen Xiezhi is working
with a female lawyer in court.

668
00:32:24,466 --> 00:32:25,670
Working with a female lawyer?

669
00:32:29,660 --> 00:32:30,940
Our son is in a relationship?

670
00:32:32,980 --> 00:32:34,380
Why are you smiling about that?

671
00:32:34,700 --> 00:32:35,810
Why can't I smile

672
00:32:35,810 --> 00:32:37,140
when my son has a girlfriend?

673
00:32:38,250 --> 00:32:39,980
Besides, that girl looks nice.

674
00:32:40,133 --> 00:32:41,490
You've seen that girl before?

675
00:32:42,010 --> 00:32:42,770
Yes.

676
00:32:43,380 --> 00:32:45,620
When I went to give a talk
at his courthouse,

677
00:32:45,700 --> 00:32:47,090
I met her.

678
00:32:47,570 --> 00:32:48,490
Her surname was Qin.

679
00:32:48,730 --> 00:32:49,980
She looked like a gentle woman.

680
00:32:50,380 --> 00:32:52,860
Back then, she kept comforting me

681
00:32:52,940 --> 00:32:54,770
and told me Shen Xiezhi would be fine.

682
00:32:55,250 --> 00:32:57,380
If there's nothing
between her and our son,

683
00:32:57,570 --> 00:32:58,940
why would she treat me so well?

684
00:33:00,980 --> 00:33:02,090
Qin?

685
00:33:02,860 --> 00:33:04,220
Why didn't I know about this person

686
00:33:04,220 --> 00:33:05,180
in Qingcheng Court?

687
00:33:05,860 --> 00:33:06,660
What does she do?

688
00:33:06,730 --> 00:33:07,900
Must you know everything

689
00:33:07,900 --> 00:33:09,700
in Qingcheng Court?

690
00:33:10,700 --> 00:33:12,140
I have that girl's WeChat.

691
00:33:12,620 --> 00:33:14,050
I've seen her Moments.

692
00:33:14,620 --> 00:33:16,180
Her face was bitten by insects.

693
00:33:16,620 --> 00:33:17,380
I even asked her

694
00:33:17,380 --> 00:33:19,340
if she wanted to get an examination
at the hospital.

695
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:22,250
It's her. Look.
Her face is full of insect bites.

696
00:33:23,050 --> 00:33:25,180
Although her face is full of bites,

697
00:33:25,700 --> 00:33:26,860
she still looks good,

698
00:33:27,010 --> 00:33:27,810
right?

699
00:33:28,940 --> 00:33:30,660
She's a good match for our son.

700
00:33:30,755 --> 00:33:32,222
A handsome man and a pretty woman.

701
00:33:32,700 --> 00:33:34,980
With his character,
it's impossible for this to be true.

702
00:33:35,660 --> 00:33:37,980
I have to verify with him one day.

703
00:33:38,900 --> 00:33:40,290
Don't cause any trouble.

704
00:33:40,620 --> 00:33:42,090
Your son hates it

705
00:33:42,090 --> 00:33:43,770
when you interfere with his matters.

706
00:33:44,050 --> 00:33:44,860
Don't ask about it.

707
00:33:46,900 --> 00:33:48,090
What did I tell you last time?

708
00:33:49,140 --> 00:33:51,940
Your son has grown up.
You need to let go.

709
00:33:52,980 --> 00:33:54,090
If I keep you in check

710
00:33:54,090 --> 00:33:55,490
every day,

711
00:33:55,660 --> 00:33:56,660
will you be happy?

712
00:33:57,180 --> 00:33:58,090
Dad, I'm happy.

713
00:33:58,090 --> 00:33:59,730
Please keep him in check.

714
00:33:59,980 --> 00:34:01,620
He is a professor at school

715
00:34:01,810 --> 00:34:03,700
and he still wants to be one
back at home.

716
00:34:05,140 --> 00:34:06,570
Enough. Stop talking. Just eat.

717
00:34:10,650 --> 00:34:12,420
(Jindian Law Firm)
(This Feng Shengli...)

718
00:34:17,690 --> 00:34:19,050
He's not picking up.

719
00:34:40,940 --> 00:34:41,820
Hello.

720
00:34:41,900 --> 00:34:44,210
The number you are calling is...

721
00:34:46,650 --> 00:34:47,740
Sorry.

722
00:34:47,933 --> 00:34:49,355
What cases are you inquiring about?

723
00:34:49,420 --> 00:34:50,300
Please come here.

724
00:34:50,530 --> 00:34:52,010
How many lawyers do you have?

725
00:34:53,050 --> 00:34:53,940
Two.

726
00:34:56,130 --> 00:34:57,260
Miss, stop.

727
00:34:57,420 --> 00:34:58,380
Don't go.

728
00:34:58,860 --> 00:35:00,130
Do you have a case?

729
00:35:00,130 --> 00:35:00,900
It's like this.

730
00:35:00,900 --> 00:35:02,650
We might be small

731
00:35:02,860 --> 00:35:03,820
but look opposite us.

732
00:35:03,900 --> 00:35:05,311
The courthouse is just opposite us.

733
00:35:05,422 --> 00:35:06,460
It's convenient for a trial.

734
00:35:06,610 --> 00:35:08,260
We want to give back to society

735
00:35:08,530 --> 00:35:10,340
and also target the community.

736
00:35:10,400 --> 00:35:12,200
There are no small cases
in the community.

737
00:35:12,311 --> 00:35:13,610
We've handled many classic cases.

738
00:35:13,980 --> 00:35:14,980
Classic cases?

739
00:35:15,740 --> 00:35:17,050
So how much do you pay

740
00:35:17,050 --> 00:35:18,300
in taxes each year?

741
00:35:18,980 --> 00:35:19,780
That's...

742
00:35:20,066 --> 00:35:21,740
I don't know.
I haven't learned about it.

743
00:35:21,740 --> 00:35:23,177
If you don't know the company's,

744
00:35:23,222 --> 00:35:24,688
I'm sure you know your personal tax.

745
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:27,980
Are you here to check the taxes?

746
00:35:28,210 --> 00:35:29,740
Show me your documents.

747
00:35:34,044 --> 00:35:35,650
You really won't be taken advantage of.

748
00:35:40,650 --> 00:35:42,380
I came here because of your fame.

749
00:35:43,090 --> 00:35:44,650
(Today, I'll be telling you)

750
00:35:44,650 --> 00:35:46,090
(a touching story.)

751
00:35:46,200 --> 00:35:48,733
(Rui's Legal Lens, Law Broadcast)
(It's called "Kindness with Fangs".)

752
00:35:49,780 --> 00:35:51,460
I know you are a small lawyer

753
00:35:51,460 --> 00:35:52,740
whose career has just started.

754
00:35:53,177 --> 00:35:55,740
However, I didn't expect you
to work in such a tough environment.

755
00:35:57,740 --> 00:35:58,690
You...

756
00:35:59,340 --> 00:36:01,570
You follow me. Are you a fan of mine?

757
00:36:03,010 --> 00:36:04,010
Not really.

758
00:36:04,650 --> 00:36:06,260
My friend came across your video

759
00:36:06,260 --> 00:36:07,170
and sent it to me.

760
00:36:07,860 --> 00:36:09,170
My friend told me

761
00:36:09,170 --> 00:36:11,460
you handle your cases uniquely.

762
00:36:11,650 --> 00:36:13,940
Your friend has good taste.

763
00:36:16,000 --> 00:36:17,940
However, the environment
is a little shabby.

764
00:36:18,530 --> 00:36:19,740
The environment...

765
00:36:21,050 --> 00:36:23,210
Are you trying to sponsor us?

766
00:36:25,650 --> 00:36:26,940
I'm just joking.

767
00:36:27,380 --> 00:36:29,010
So? What are you inquiring about?

768
00:36:29,155 --> 00:36:30,490
I want to file for a divorce.

769
00:36:31,130 --> 00:36:32,490
Cars, properties, and money.

770
00:36:32,490 --> 00:36:34,050
I won't give anything to that jerk!

771
00:36:39,333 --> 00:36:41,200
(Jindian Law Firm)
He fails in everything

772
00:36:41,288 --> 00:36:42,610
and only knows how to eat.

773
00:36:43,090 --> 00:36:44,900
Even if I raise a salted fish,

774
00:36:45,420 --> 00:36:47,740
I'll still get fish sauce
in the aquarium.

775
00:36:48,090 --> 00:36:49,130
However,

776
00:36:50,010 --> 00:36:51,260
he actually cheated on me.

777
00:36:54,420 --> 00:36:55,260
Ms. Ding,

778
00:36:55,260 --> 00:36:57,420
your husband cheated on you, right?

779
00:36:57,690 --> 00:36:58,420
May I ask

780
00:36:58,420 --> 00:37:00,090
if you have any evidence gathered

781
00:37:00,090 --> 00:37:02,010
that helps us in
fighting for more assets?

782
00:37:04,380 --> 00:37:05,300
No.

783
00:37:06,380 --> 00:37:07,530
He is sly.

784
00:37:07,530 --> 00:37:09,900
He always deletes
the chat history on WeChat.

785
00:37:10,300 --> 00:37:11,650
I followed him a few times

786
00:37:12,690 --> 00:37:13,860
but I found nothing.

787
00:37:16,911 --> 00:37:18,088
Forget it.

788
00:37:18,422 --> 00:37:19,680
I don't want to think about it.

789
00:37:19,690 --> 00:37:20,980
I can't wait any longer.

790
00:37:21,490 --> 00:37:22,690
He doesn't make any money,

791
00:37:22,690 --> 00:37:24,050
and I pay for all his expenses.

792
00:37:24,050 --> 00:37:26,533
He is even staying in a house
I bought before we got married.

793
00:37:26,755 --> 00:37:28,650
I bought the house myself
before I got married.

794
00:37:28,650 --> 00:37:29,940
It is under my name.

795
00:37:30,066 --> 00:37:31,650
It hasn't been three years
since we got married.

796
00:37:31,650 --> 00:37:33,650
It counts as my personal assets
before marriage, right?

797
00:37:33,690 --> 00:37:34,900
That's true in principle.

798
00:37:42,377 --> 00:37:44,733
These are all the details
of our income and expenses

799
00:37:44,820 --> 00:37:46,610
since we got together.

800
00:37:46,730 --> 00:37:49,000
You just need to submit it
to the judge before the trial.

801
00:37:49,050 --> 00:37:49,860
This...

802
00:37:49,860 --> 00:37:52,010
Milk tea receipts, meal receipts...

803
00:37:52,170 --> 00:37:53,490
Even gluten sticks?

804
00:37:53,490 --> 00:37:54,690
I'm an accountant.

805
00:37:54,911 --> 00:37:56,420
I have a habit of tracking my expenses.

806
00:37:56,733 --> 00:37:58,820
I can see that you're
quite a detail-oriented person.

807
00:38:00,511 --> 00:38:02,933
Draft the representation agreement
as soon as possible.

808
00:38:03,022 --> 00:38:04,577
I'll sign it and pay you the deposit.

809
00:38:04,650 --> 00:38:05,940
I can't wait any longer.

810
00:38:10,820 --> 00:38:11,780
Also,

811
00:38:12,340 --> 00:38:14,340
I'll give you
this month's utility bills

812
00:38:14,340 --> 00:38:15,610
before we go to court.

813
00:38:15,711 --> 00:38:17,288
I still need to work,
so I'll be leaving.

814
00:38:17,311 --> 00:38:18,333
Call me if you need anything.

815
00:38:18,350 --> 00:38:19,210
Ms. Ding, don't worry.

816
00:38:19,210 --> 00:38:20,920
With these receipts
and expenditure details,

817
00:38:20,977 --> 00:38:22,420
I won't let you lose a single cent.

818
00:38:32,210 --> 00:38:33,340
Where are you?

819
00:38:33,466 --> 00:38:34,820
I'm at the market at the junction.

820
00:38:35,570 --> 00:38:36,530
Come and find me.

821
00:38:36,530 --> 00:38:37,888
What's going on with you?

822
00:38:37,911 --> 00:38:39,570
You just vanish as you wish.

823
00:38:39,570 --> 00:38:41,733
The judge and I
have been looking for you for so long.

824
00:38:43,010 --> 00:38:44,460
Fine. Wait there and don't move.

825
00:38:44,740 --> 00:38:45,690
I'll be there.

826
00:38:52,020 --> 00:38:55,220
(Supermarket Exit, Supermarket Entrance)

827
00:38:56,260 --> 00:38:57,460
What's going on with you?

828
00:38:58,210 --> 00:38:59,650
I lied for you

829
00:38:59,755 --> 00:39:00,900
and did what you told me to.

830
00:39:01,130 --> 00:39:02,490
Why did you just refuse to see me?

831
00:39:03,050 --> 00:39:04,610
I've been busy in the last two days.

832
00:39:04,610 --> 00:39:05,820
I didn't get a signal.

833
00:39:05,820 --> 00:39:08,260
No signal?
Your phone has always been switched off.

834
00:39:10,460 --> 00:39:11,860
Do you not have so much money?

835
00:39:12,377 --> 00:39:14,610
If you are incapable,
just don't pay the 350,000 yuan.

836
00:39:14,980 --> 00:39:16,210
Why must you act tough

837
00:39:16,244 --> 00:39:17,466
and add another 100,000 yuan?

838
00:39:17,980 --> 00:39:18,940
You don't understand.

839
00:39:19,260 --> 00:39:21,210
That is the most important part.

840
00:39:22,090 --> 00:39:23,610
I know. You want to write an IOU

841
00:39:23,610 --> 00:39:25,130
so they don't contact you again.

842
00:39:25,530 --> 00:39:26,490
Where's the IOU?

843
00:39:27,300 --> 00:39:29,610
You didn't transfer the money.
How do I give you the IOU?

844
00:39:29,610 --> 00:39:31,380
You didn't give me the bank account.

845
00:39:32,022 --> 00:39:33,460
I'll transfer the money immediately.

846
00:39:33,740 --> 00:39:35,010
When can I get the IOU?

847
00:39:35,420 --> 00:39:36,740
Transfer the money

848
00:39:36,740 --> 00:39:38,010
and you'll get it immediately.

849
00:39:39,288 --> 00:39:40,377
You don't know how difficult

850
00:39:40,380 --> 00:39:42,190
it was to find you
in the last few days.

851
00:39:42,260 --> 00:39:42,860
I wonder why

852
00:39:42,860 --> 00:39:44,340
I accepted your case back then.

853
00:39:45,010 --> 00:39:45,980
I'm so unlucky.

854
00:39:48,530 --> 00:39:50,420
I think
you are the right person for the job.

855
00:39:51,010 --> 00:39:53,260
You look pretty on the outside,

856
00:39:53,690 --> 00:39:54,740
but I'm guessing

857
00:39:54,900 --> 00:39:57,222
that you're also
in a difficult situation just like me.

858
00:39:57,530 --> 00:39:58,740
You are just like me.

859
00:39:58,866 --> 00:40:01,844
You are worried about losing your income
when you're down for one day.

860
00:40:01,980 --> 00:40:03,666
You either live in a village in the city

861
00:40:03,690 --> 00:40:05,900
or a small shared rental unit.

862
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:07,940
If you have money,
you'll eat in a restaurant.

863
00:40:08,050 --> 00:40:09,800
If you don't,
you'll eat instant noodles.

864
00:40:09,940 --> 00:40:11,380
After giving your family money,

865
00:40:11,380 --> 00:40:13,111
you'll be worried
about your utility bills.

866
00:40:13,940 --> 00:40:15,420
Can you say no?

867
00:40:15,466 --> 00:40:17,460
Do you dare to get sick?
Do you have a way out?

868
00:40:17,460 --> 00:40:19,130
Enough. Stop talking nonsense.

869
00:40:19,130 --> 00:40:20,955
Are you going
to transfer me money or not?

870
00:40:21,340 --> 00:40:22,650
Besides, we are not the same.

871
00:40:22,650 --> 00:40:23,780
If my grandmother is sick,

872
00:40:23,780 --> 00:40:25,660
I'd donate as many kidneys to her
as she needs.

873
00:40:25,711 --> 00:40:27,420
Fine. You're filial.

874
00:40:28,900 --> 00:40:30,090
To give money

875
00:40:30,090 --> 00:40:31,380
to your grandmother,

876
00:40:31,900 --> 00:40:34,050
you still accepted my case.

877
00:40:37,100 --> 00:40:38,890
I transferred
the representation fees to you.

878
00:40:39,260 --> 00:40:40,690
Your mission is complete now.

879
00:40:40,900 --> 00:40:43,460
Only the account and IOU are needed.

880
00:40:43,460 --> 00:40:44,860
The rest is none of your business.

881
00:40:46,090 --> 00:40:46,820
Oh.

882
00:40:46,820 --> 00:40:48,460
Judge Shen wants to talk with you.

883
00:40:48,690 --> 00:40:49,940
When are you free?

884
00:40:55,820 --> 00:40:57,340
Why do all of you like

885
00:40:57,420 --> 00:40:58,650
being nosy?

886
00:41:14,170 --> 00:41:15,010
This...

887
00:41:15,340 --> 00:41:16,380
Why have you passed out?

888
00:41:16,380 --> 00:41:17,650
Are you kidding me?

889
00:41:17,888 --> 00:41:19,460
What's going on? Someone passed out.

890
00:41:27,500 --> 00:41:29,060
(Emergency)

891
00:41:48,900 --> 00:41:50,650
Why didn't you tell me that you're sick?

892
00:41:50,700 --> 00:41:51,900
I'm your representative lawyer.

893
00:41:51,900 --> 00:41:53,490
I have the right to know your condition.

894
00:41:55,022 --> 00:41:56,844
Why did you hide your condition from me?

895
00:42:00,570 --> 00:42:02,210
What's the point of telling?

896
00:42:02,570 --> 00:42:04,260
Do you know

897
00:42:05,711 --> 00:42:07,422
what our family's annual salary is

898
00:42:07,900 --> 00:42:09,490
besides mine?

899
00:42:14,860 --> 00:42:15,820
When I was young,

900
00:42:16,740 --> 00:42:18,530
as long as our family
had a little money,

901
00:42:20,050 --> 00:42:21,690
my father would spend it on me.

902
00:42:23,980 --> 00:42:25,460
Other people say he was biased,

903
00:42:27,130 --> 00:42:29,010
but he told them he was sure

904
00:42:30,050 --> 00:42:31,420
that I'd be successful.

905
00:42:31,780 --> 00:42:32,860
I could make money

906
00:42:33,740 --> 00:42:34,940
and repay the family.

907
00:42:35,933 --> 00:42:38,488
My brother has started paying me
since he started working.

908
00:42:40,740 --> 00:42:42,780
However, he also earns a salary.

909
00:42:44,022 --> 00:42:46,622
He doesn't even have enough
to support his own family.

910
00:42:46,711 --> 00:42:48,533
My sister-in-law wanted a divorce
and tried to take the kids away

911
00:42:48,555 --> 00:42:49,555
on multiple occasions.

912
00:42:49,940 --> 00:42:51,530
However, my sister stopped her.

913
00:42:51,740 --> 00:42:53,610
My sister said
she'd pay me in the future,

914
00:42:53,844 --> 00:42:55,777
so it's no longer
my brother's responsibility.

915
00:42:57,266 --> 00:42:59,490
However, she is also
an employee who earns a salary.

916
00:43:00,820 --> 00:43:01,980
How much money does she have?

917
00:43:14,620 --> 00:43:18,080
♪All the little things
between you and me♪

918
00:43:18,080 --> 00:43:20,760
♪Woven into our lives♪

919
00:43:21,610 --> 00:43:23,590
♪The building blocks of life♪

920
00:43:23,590 --> 00:43:25,290
♪Shape the sky above us♪

921
00:43:25,290 --> 00:43:27,450
♪Are you doing alright?♪

922
00:43:27,770 --> 00:43:30,450
♪What are you struggling for?♪

923
00:43:31,330 --> 00:43:35,150
♪Some questions weigh like mountains♪

924
00:43:35,530 --> 00:43:40,380
♪How do we piece life back together?♪

925
00:43:40,940 --> 00:43:45,130
♪So hate can fade
and love feels new again♪

926
00:43:45,130 --> 00:43:48,200
♪Reclaim the barren parts of life♪

927
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:54,570
♪Walking this road
together, still hoping♪

928
00:43:55,360 --> 00:44:00,420
♪Let me be the wind at dawn♪

929
00:44:00,720 --> 00:44:04,690
♪Blowing away all the pain♪

930
00:44:04,920 --> 00:44:09,900
♪Let me be the balance
that holds the weight♪

931
00:44:10,320 --> 00:44:14,880
♪Where fairness stands♪

932
00:44:15,350 --> 00:44:17,590
♪Within every heart♪

933
00:44:17,590 --> 00:44:20,240
♪So many voices calling♪

934
00:44:20,500 --> 00:44:24,790
♪Struggling, lost,
waiting for an answer♪

935
00:44:24,790 --> 00:44:27,140
♪Light up the lamps♪

936
00:44:27,140 --> 00:44:29,810
♪To answer those voices♪

937
00:44:30,120 --> 00:44:32,240
♪You deserve to be happy♪

938
00:44:32,240 --> 00:44:34,990
♪Loud and clear♪

939
00:44:34,990 --> 00:44:37,310
♪All the little things♪

940
00:44:37,310 --> 00:44:40,010
♪Woven into our lives♪

941
00:44:40,830 --> 00:44:42,880
♪The building blocks of life♪

942
00:44:42,880 --> 00:44:44,590
♪Shape the sky above us♪

943
00:44:44,590 --> 00:44:47,040
♪Are you doing alright?♪

944
00:44:47,040 --> 00:44:49,150
♪What are you struggling for?♪

945
00:44:49,400 --> 00:44:51,530
♪Some questions♪

946
00:44:52,100 --> 00:44:54,800
♪Weigh like mountains♪

947
00:44:57,690 --> 00:45:02,840
♪Let me be the wind at dawn♪

948
00:45:03,120 --> 00:45:07,130
♪Blowing away all the pain♪

949
00:45:07,310 --> 00:45:12,360
♪Let me be the balance
that holds the weight♪

950
00:45:12,730 --> 00:45:16,430
♪Where fairness stands♪

951
00:45:16,600 --> 00:45:19,680
♪Within the law♪

952
00:45:20,840 --> 00:45:29,520
♪And within every heart♪
